{"tid":2391302,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"地中海泥芯揭 16 萬年來撒哈拉沙漠曾多次出現草原","createTime":"2021-02-02T06:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T07:45:14.000Z","uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca128b97eb622a0d3e29af5362cdd0067ee47a11","tid":2391302,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcJz6bU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcJz6bU.jpg&h=9564604e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撒哈拉沙漠大部分地區數千年前可能是一片綠色草原，這都可由石器時代洞穴石刻與壁畫上的史前長頸鹿、鱷魚和人類游泳作佐證。<br />\n<br />\n最新刊於《自然地球科學》的研究，從地中海沉積物核與氣候模型模擬對 16 萬年以來撒哈拉沙漠與北非環境變化，提出更多更詳細背景&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/地中海泥芯揭-16-萬年來撒哈拉沙漠曾多次出現草原/?fbclid=IwAR0-zhT3WRVJyZhsr4d0sDbg8OLUdPZr--UndCc-KnVYf6gD1m-1L1NEroo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E6%B3%A5%E8%8A%AF%E6%8F%AD-16-%E8%90%AC%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%92%92%E5%93%88%E6%8B%89%E6%B2%99%E6%BC%A0%E6%9B%BE%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E8%8D%89%E5%8E%9F%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0-zhT3WRVJyZhsr4d0sDbg8OLUdPZr--UndCc-KnVYf6gD1m-1L1NEroo&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=8e2969f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fnature%2F%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%AD%E6%B5%B7%E6%B3%A5%E8%8A%AF%E6%8F%AD-16-%E8%90%AC%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%92%92%E5%93%88%E6%8B%89%E6%B2%99%E6%BC%A0%E6%9B%BE%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E8%8D%89%E5%8E%9F%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0-zhT3WRVJyZhsr4d0sDbg8OLUdPZr--UndCc-KnVYf6gD1m-1L1NEroo&h=1b11325e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/nature/地中海泥芯揭-16-萬年來撒哈拉沙漠曾多次出現草原/?fbclid=IwAR0-zhT3WRVJyZhsr4d0sDbg8OLUdPZr--UndCc-KnVYf6gD1m-1L1NEroo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n少歌劇場版要成神了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UtHw8r0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUtHw8r0.png&h=300cf3b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a 